 Todolist Project

### About the Project

This is a **Todolist web page** built using **HTML and CSS**. The goal of this project is to create a visually appealing page that motivates users to complete daily tasks.

The background image sets a calm tone, and the content is structured with headings, motivational text, and a call-to-action button.

